996年取消所有限制"},{"pid":"72fd6a4db20a01df1c3cbd9a5db7ebc42d3f01ca","tid":683061,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"以前大學上大通啲堂話阿斯巴甜好似有副作用，不過唔記得咗點解後來可以加入食品到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5c85cdfb943f6eafdc5b8291934c5ee2687bd8","tid":683061,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72fd6a4db20a01df1c3cbd9a5db7ebc42d3f01ca","tid":683061,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"以前大學上大通啲堂話阿斯巴甜好似有副作用，不過唔記得咗點解後來可以加入食品到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"後面果PART好緊要<br />\n你快D記返佢啦<br />\n記得返話比我知"},{"pid":"f26e79a8f01d26ec97bef824012851f41a35c09f","tid":683061,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72fd6a4db20a01df1c3cbd9a5db7ebc42d3f01ca","tid":683061,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"以前大學上大通啲堂話阿斯巴甜好似有副作用，不過唔記得咗點解後來可以加入食品到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"任何野攝取過量都對健康唔好<br />\n<br />\n好似每日每人飲超過廿罐350ml zero 先會超過世衛建議劑量<br />\n普通紅色可樂一罐超過30g糖 飲多過2罐已過世衛建議攝取糖既份量<br />\n<br />\n咁我寧願飲zero"},{"pid":"84e77cd41317c087a6a5c0a12823d385b6275a1e","tid":683061,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"次次飲親無糖可樂都會想嘔<br />\n關唔關啲代糖事"},{"pid":"12bf31ddf100c7d28075f17bb7a73f358ee7afa2","tid":683061,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"我飲完黑罐會頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係幾似真可樂 我都想用黎替紅罐"},{"pid":"78c9e745de2bfce0c1633237021baca5641f3880","tid":683061,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/